cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual place recognition using deep networks. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as place recognition is an important task for robots navigating in different environments. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes different approaches for improving deep network performance. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply as the paper deals with improving the ability of machines to recognize places. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with processing sequences of images.
